Engaged Cryptera Chain Signals for a bridge exploit trace. Their experience (28 years 426+ cases) showed in the structured workflow and detailed explanations. Multi-layer analysis mapped the cross-chain movement but jurisdictional and timing issues prevented full restitution.
Appreciated the education on bridge risks smart contract verification and preventive steps like multi-sig and regular audits. Reports were thorough with visuals making complex paths easier to follow. No false hope given upfront which built trust. Good option if you value transparency and learning. 4.1/5.
